divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife & I were watching the Tapps Island firework display, when 5 orange globes appeared in the eastern sky. These globes moved like an airplane, but had no collison lights flashing like the other planes in the sky. Then one by one they would disappear from the sky flying straight up.
Summary: My Wife & I saw 5 orange globes apprear in the eastern sky
trends: There have been no other sightings in Lake Tapps
